974302,3262]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=15729731]艾雨kk[/uid] (2026-04-01 14:50):[/b]<br/><br/>第一时间干进去了，今天听狼大的t+0给我干出来不少盈利[/quote]<br/>哪天听我的是亏钱的？[s:ac:反对]", "lou": 1705, "content_length": 23, "reply_to": 863101892, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775026430}, {"pid": 863104103, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 29, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 15:06", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们买啥都行。我做的是期货[s:ac:哭笑] 随便一层仓位上个12倍杠杆  1个点的波动就够了<br/>而且这是稳稳的1个点[s:ac:计划通]", "lou": 1706, "content_length": 82, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775027175}, {"pid": 863192026, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 62, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 10:27", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "暂时不要急着买 目前没发现买点", "lou": 1707, "content_length": 28, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775096861}, {"pid": 863194258, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 10:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "其实跟外围关系不大了  这里是我们自己的循环空间。主要还是关口位置缩太大的量了  只能下来蓄势下一次", "lou": 1708, "content_length": 92, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775097729}, {"pid": 863194775, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 10:45", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863194030,45974302,3286]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=6313142]暮残[/uid] (2026-04-02 10:40):[/b]<br/><br/>又是缩量拉银行，科技45°向下<br/>继续回3900绞肉[/quote]<br/>今天到不了3900  灰兔子不是说了 3929么 目前先看这里的支撑。<br/>目前看这量能急杀不了的", "lou": 1709, "content_length": 81, "reply_to": 863194030, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775097931}, {"pid": 863195744, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 28, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 10:51", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "昨天说的期货 今天有没有人做的？9点反向一卖  直接吃大肉 昨天是多金空油  早上9点准备空金多油 根本不用犹豫和考虑", "lou": 1710, "content_length": 102, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775098274}, {"pid": 863196119, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 10:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863195758,45974302,3288]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65607701]multporn[/uid] (2026-04-02 10:51):[/b]<br/><br/>机构没砸吧，机构真砸直接3800了。[/quote]<br/>我刚刚问了 没砸", "lou": 1711, "content_length": 19, "reply_to": 863195758, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775098413}, {"pid": 863196530, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 18, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 10:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863196190,45974302,3288]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66982010]椰果奶茶配椰果[/uid] (2026-04-02 10:54):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:委屈]买的黄金股，现在不知道要不要跑，还在观望[/quote]<br/>股票受到里面资金影响太大了  我不做建议 但是之后黄金还有4820以上的位置冲击  你们可以自己参考", "lou": 1712, "content_length": 91, "reply_to": 863196190, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775098573}, {"pid": 863196920, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 10:58", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863196375,45974302,3288]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67072821]最后一哈[/uid] (2026-04-02 10:55):[/b]<br/><br/>太看得起楼里的兄弟们了，现在这行情玩期货可能连新手红利都吃不上就亏完了[s:ac:哭笑]，楼里真有人看你说个话就无脑梭哈的，昨天看多金就梭哈晓程的还不多嘛，甚至你说国内黄金股都是垃圾蹭子这么多次了还有人不信邪的[/quote]<br/>如果做黄金ETF是能吃肉的  股票确实博弈感太强了 。很难受  里面各种预判的预判。还受大盘影响 还有量化 不好玩", "lou": 1713, "content_length": 102, "reply_to": 863196375, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775098721}, {"pid": 863197100, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 10, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 10:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863196544,45974302,3288]